title: fanoutqa: What was the population in 1990 of the countries that have successfully landed on the moon? (f71b3ba07d3af7d6)

chat_history.content: What was the population in 1990 of the countries that have successfully landed on the moon?

I'm afraid there is no country that has landed on the moon.

The United States of America has, however, been successful in landing on the moon, but only as part of the Apollo program.

If you would like to know the population of the USA in 1990, I'd be happy to help you.
